      <p align="center"><a name="top"></a><b><font size="5"><font face="Georgia"><font
 color="#3e1f00">Middleware Support for Cross-Disability Access</font></font></font></b>
      </p>
      <p align="center"><b><i><font color="#008000">Project sponsored by Office of Naval Research (ONR) as part of the DOD Multidisciplinary University Research  Initiative (MURI) and NSF Career Award ANI-9875988</font></i></b>
      </p>
